high_descs: Turn right and walk to the larger sofa on the right.
Pick up the black gaming controller from the couch.
Turn to the sidetable on the left.
Put the controller on the sidetable.
Turn around and walk to the shelf.
Pick up the black gaming controller from the shelf.
Turn around to walk back to the sidetable.
Put the gaming controller next to the other controller on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the two gaming controllers on the side table.

high_descs: Turn around in the hall go left and locate the joystick on the sofa.
Pick the controller from the sofa and turn around in the hall.
Turn around with joystick and go nearby to sidetable.
Place the controller on the sidetable.
Turn around in the hall go straight and locate another joystick on the shelf.
Pick the controller from the shelf.
Turn around left and move straight and go nearby to the sidetable.
Place the second controller on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Pick two controller from sofa and SideTable in the hall and place them on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the sofa on your right.
Pick up controller from the sofa.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the side table.
Place controller on the side table.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the shelf.
Pick up controller from the sofa.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the side table.
Place controller on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Collecting controller from different places and arranging them on a side table.
